{"type":"text","timestamp":1775849187751,"sessionID":"ses_28725112effeLv38OgxzcMAJ8A","part":{"id":"prt_d78dc198f001qaM4fuJ1KvkGrm","messageID":"msg_d78dbff48001i3BD0NBVcHWGm9","sessionID":"ses_28725112effeLv38OgxzcMAJ8A","type":"text","text":"## AR-010 вҖ” Router дјҡиҜқз®ЎзҗҶ Summary\n\n### Completed вң“\n\n**Core Implementation:**\n- Session configuration with all options (`SessionEnabled`, `SessionTimeout`, `SessionCookieName`, `SessionMaxActive`, `SessionCookieSecure`, `SessionCookieHTTPOnly`, `SessionCookieDomain`, `SessionCleanupInterval`)\n- Session data structures: `Session` struct, `SessionStore` interface, `MemorySessionStore` (thread-safe)\n- Session ID generation using UUID v4\n- Session middleware: cookie/header extraction, new session creation, activity tracking\n- Session affinity (sticky sessions): backend key stored in session, routes to same backend\n- Session expiration with sliding expiration\n- Periodic cleanup goroutine\n- Cookie configuration (Secure, HttpOnly, Domain, Path)\n- Session metrics: `router_sessions_active`, `router_sessions_created_total`, `router_sessions_expired_total`, `router_session_duration_seconds`\n- Graceful shutdown integration\n\n### Deferred (Out of Scope from Design)\n\nThese were explicitly excluded from the original proposal:\n- **Distributed session store** (Redis, etcd) вҖ” future enhancement\n- **Session persistence to Kubernetes CRD** вҖ” future enhancement\n- **Session replication across router instances**\n- **OIDC/OAuth2 session integration** вҖ” uses existing auth middleware\n\n### Build Status\n- вң“ `go build ./pkg/router/...` вҖ” compiles successfully","time":{"start":1775849187750,"end":1775849187750}}}
